text: Outstanding pizza,....an incredibly delicious combination of tastes. Service was courteous and FAST....and this was on a Friday night. Loved this restaurant.....highly recommended!

text: Wonderful little pizza shop. Reasonably priced, very good selection of topping and crust. Very good service and friendly staff.
